Description: Phoning-home version checks should be disabled in Debian packages
Author: Sandro Knau√ü <bugs@ssandroknauss.de>
Origin: debian
Bug-debian: http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=721341
